Use Test-Driven development while avoiding regressions across linters and tests for changes in src. 
New implementations or modifications to code shall include writing tests by first researching the API spec. https://api.endorlabs.com/download/openapiv2.swagger.json
These tests shall be meaningful and appropriately categorized. 
Must maintain architectural consistency with the rest of the implementations
Consider the threat model and make necessary changes for secure outcomes.
Balance DX, maintainability with correctness to API Spec contract.
Commit locally with a meaningful commit message.
